<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Kim Kardashian is known for catering to those closest to her.</p>

<p>And the 39-year-old decided to host a gathering for her 'Lifers' on Tuesday evening, which consisted of plenty of confectionary treats and an intimate dinner.</p>

<p>Meanwhile, sisters Kylie Jenner, Kourtney Kardashian, and mom Kris attempted to make the most of their night with boardgames, personalized donuts, and decadent snacks.</p>

