<p>Kim's 'Lifers,' as the reality TV sensation explained in an interview with Fat Mascara last month, are 'a group of seven of us' who have 'been best friends since pre-school.'</p>

<p>This 'group of seven' happens to include Allison Statter, whom Kim just recently launched an entire KKW Beauty collection with.</p>

